    "en": {
      "title": "179 people die in floods in Assam, India",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the report released by India's Assam State Disaster Management Authority, five more people were killed in severe floods that hit the state on Sunday, taking the total number of deaths due to floods in the state to 179.",
        "Across 26 districts, over 1.83 million people are still affected by the floods.",
        "Heavy rains accompanied by storms hit the region for the first time since last month, affecting millions of people in Assam."
      ],
